# =============================================================================
# Engineering pipeline — transient state (never commit)
# =============================================================================
# Runtime DB and progress tracking — machine-local state, not source of truth.
.pipeline/manifest.db
.pipeline/progress.md

# Per-slice phase artifacts — inter-agent handoff data, rebuild on re-run.
# Pattern: .pipeline/1/, .pipeline/2/, .pipeline/42/, etc.
.pipeline/[0-9]*/
.pipeline/[0-9][0-9]*/
.pipeline/[0-9][0-9][0-9]*/

# =============================================================================
# Engineering pipeline — source of truth (DO commit these)
# =============================================================================
# Everything not matched above under .pipeline/ is committed, including:
# .pipeline/CONTEXT.md          ← project identity, written by auk-1 once
# .pipeline/ISSUES.md           ← GitHub fallback when offline
# .pipeline/CHANGE_SCOPE.md     ← written by auk-1 for update/pipeline-update cycles
# .pipeline/RETROFIT_SCOPE.md   ← written by auk-1 for retrofit cycles
# .pipeline/prototype/          ← poc.py + deps.py + FINDINGS.md
# .pipeline/orientation/        ← MODULE_MAP, DEPENDENCY_MAP, CONVENTIONS (from auk-0-orient)

.llm_budget.json
